{"tid":712752,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"今次我哋聽Joey -容祖兒","createTime":"2018-06-22T10:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T21:40:27.000Z","uid":71166,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d6f9663ac9d708403c28edc42b1f3d86de4021","tid":712752,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"揀一啲弘有回憶嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5cc066804ca449914b960dc35d192882c772f9","tid":712752,"uid":71166,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">信今生愛過</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FFZwyjGkctQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFFZwyjGkctQ&d=PuaKngDH%2FZM%2BerZQRb5l9TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=36a3a0b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FFZwyjGkctQ</a><br />\n天明時 在大地前角逐過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">然而公主日落前替你做過</span><br />\n<br />\n盡力做華麗一幕 得一次亦算多<br />\n別問誰有錯 就算開花不結果<br />\n<br />\n來 我應該快樂 而遺憾不應該太多<br />\n來又急促 走也匆忙<br />\n或者之間的故事太多<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">來 我祝福你快樂<br />\n和誰行盡一生得到極多<br />\n還叫我接受年月荒唐<br />\n不相信誰 都相信曾愛過</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d16e88ecde0653750f99802cdeb146fc9a03bbf","tid":712752,"uid":56716,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"煙霞"},{"pid":"35360597c3ae9ee8be89934ae6e1a64951ca3869","tid":712752,"uid":166992,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:46:01.000Z","msg":"痛愛"},{"pid":"86eab1bc09c4cb884f000dab7c69b45df216fb34","tid":712752,"uid":71166,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:46:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心病</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WggyiKCEXh0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWggyiKCEXh0&d=PuaKngDH%2FZM%2BerZQRb5l9TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f196efc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WggyiKCEXh0</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">再勉強　撐一撐　大病就消散<br />\n要是還未淡　還未慣　還在怨　還再嘆　再病發註定更慘</span><br />\n假使命運任我揀　狂瀾能力挽　怎可因病而偷懶<br />\n存亡聚散　靠我努力渡難關"},{"pid":"3ad2547a11137018091f730bab07bf198d257715","tid":712752,"uid":71166,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2d16e88ecde0653750f99802cdeb146fc9a03bbf","tid":712752,"uid":56716,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"煙霞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"吉bee<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YUJObfMtq7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYUJObfMtq7c&d=PuaKngDH%2FZM%2BerZQRb5l9TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7ed758c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YUJObfMtq7c</a><br />\n遊遍了天下　前路的風景　蓋著了煙霞<br />\n蒙閉的雙眼　<span style=\"color: red;\">未明白拈上你是何代價<br />\n彼此亦另有他<br />\n神秘的煙霞　誰認清真假</span><br />\n你別要用我受不住的鼻音跟我說話<br />\n令我的心軟化<br />\n證實我真心想有火花"},{"pid":"2ab4f74550dda447096e0f371b5c5b8f8a5ae442","tid":712752,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ad2547a11137018091f730bab07bf198d257715","tid":712752,"uid":71166,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2d16e88ecde0653750f99802cdeb146fc9a03bbf","tid":712752,"uid":56716,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"煙霞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"吉bee<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YUJObfMtq7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYUJObfMtq7c&d=PuaKngDH%2FZM%2BerZQRb5l9TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7ed758c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YUJObfMtq7c</a><br />\n遊遍了天下　前路的風景　蓋著了煙霞<br />\n蒙閉的雙眼　<span style=\"color: red;\">未明白拈上你是何代價<br />\n彼此亦另有他<br />\n神秘的煙霞　誰認清