red;\">再勉強　撐一撐　大病就消散<br />\n要是還未淡　還未慣　還在怨　還再嘆　再病發註定更慘</span><br />\n假使命運任我揀　狂瀾能力挽　怎可因病而偷懶<br />\n存亡聚散　靠我努力渡難關"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"幸福傷風素首廣告歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾聽晒成首歌就覺得同賣感冒藥完全無關"},{"pid":"be95359a27becb8f69eb8e3033b5421e9b4fd34a","tid":712752,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d828f89ea97f9b8edc45fa7f5d4a27d5f18bb4","tid":712752,"uid":29929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"Lm <br />\n幾欣賞呢個P.O.<br />\nJoey我敢講舊歌10首有9首都好好聽"},{"pid":"86d7c4b4c744d5228858a8ee67b1792b6955ac7d","tid":712752,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T16:57:44.000Z","msg":"03072018- 伏在你身說找到更喜愛的人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一拍兩散</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q8nWYc3_h3M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq8nWYc3_h3M&d=PuaKngDH%2FZM%2BerZQRb5l9TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=dbaa731c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q8nWYc3_h3M</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當初的我為了你　圍滿著好友　日夜怪你愛不夠　還驚你風流<br />\n然後到我內疚　任旁人來認購　恨你沒有問情由便放我走<br />\n<br />\n我卻要忠變奸　斗膽一腳踏兩船<br />\n想上岸時又晏　無面目再解釋　<br />\n自廢了承諾是否太斗膽</span>"}]}